originalText.text: Needed emergency dental work and Dr. Kim did a fantastic job, he worked on my tooth until the bite was perfect. Have been going to this dental group for years and usually see Dr. Klein for dental work and Helen for cleanings- they are all really great!

originalText.text: I cannot say enough good things about West End Dental Associates. My family and I have been patients there for over 20 years.  The office is run as a close-knit team.  They are caring and organized, and always able to find a prompt appointment spot for me in urgent situations. The providers are highly skilled and caring, and all specialties are conveniently under one roof.  Yesterday, I had a semi-urgent situation requiring Dr. Miles the Oral Surgeon (a highly skilled, experienced and thoughtful oral surgeon).  Dr. Sacks went above and beyond to keep her eyes open for a cancelation or earlier opening, and they were able to fit me in on the same day!  I am grateful for the  excellent and sincere care I have received all these years, and my teeth are thankful as well.
